public interface Listable

Interface used to tie an action into ListTag 3.0 (known for a while as "new List Tag"). This interface allows the List*Helper classes to interact with the action to retrieve the data to show on the page.

See the Spacewalk wiki for more information on how to work with ListTag 3.0.
